<node id="Water Buffaloes">
  <data key="d0">Water Buffaloes</data>
  <data key="d1">creature</data>
  <data key="d2">Water buffaloes are a type of bovine identified as major reservoirs of human infection for Schistosoma japonicum in China.&lt;SEP&gt;Animals in which the detection of antibodies against S. Japonicum takes place.&lt;SEP&gt;Bovine animals in the Philippines found to have S. Japonicum infection.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c33d09b8957ec6de1ecb70a00240f29b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-213dd01df1213177a022c154bb9c179e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-12418866e7efdfc1aa9ada51674dfa7e</data>
