  <data key="d0">qPCR-Based Study</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">A study using quantitative Polymerase Chain Reaction that indicated 51% of carabao were Schistosoma japonicum-positive, contrasting with conventional methods.</data>
