  <data key="d0">Conventional Copro-Parasitological Techniques</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Traditional diagnostic methods used to detect parasitic infections from fecal samples, known for their low diagnostic sensitivity in detecting Schistosoma japonicum in carabao.</data>
