  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The process by which the disease schistosomiasis japonicum is spread, particularly concerning the role of reservoir hosts like carabao.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c33d09b8957ec6de1ecb70a00240f29b</data>
