<node id="Validated Real-Time PCR (qPCR)">
  <data key="d0">Validated Real-Time PCR (qPCR)</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">A highly sensitive diagnostic tool used in the pilot survey that, along with FEA-SD, revealed a high prevalence of Schistosoma japonicum in carabao, offering more accurate diagnosis.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c33d09b8957ec6de1ecb70a00240f29b</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
