  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Public health strategies and efforts aimed at managing and reducing the incidence of schistosomiasis, which may be significantly impacted by new findings regarding bovine transmission.&lt;SEP&gt;A public health strategy aimed at reducing the burden of schistosomiasis, relying heavily on mass drug administration.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c33d09b8957ec6de1ecb70a00240f29b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a197e3ca4d2489f92b9e283070c072f4</data>
