  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">A drug used in selective chemotherapy, a main strategy in China's National Schistosomiasis Control Program.&lt;SEP&gt;A comparatively cheap drug used in mass drug administration for the treatment of schistosomiasis.&lt;SEP&gt;Praziquantel is a specific drug used in mass chemotherapy.&lt;SEP&gt;Praziquantel is an anthelminthic drug used for the treatment of schistosomiasis.</data>
