  <data key="d1">creature</data>
  <data key="d2">Dogs are animals that may be reservoir hosts.&lt;SEP&gt;Animals that can serve as reservoir hosts for Haplorchis pumilio, targeted by control programs.&lt;SEP&gt;Dogs are animals that require regular anthelmintic treatment as part of integrated FZT control programs.&lt;SEP&gt;These are animals from which faeces were collected for diagnostic evaluation.</data>
