<node id="Infectious Bursal Disease">
  <data key="d0">Infectious Bursal Disease</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Infectious Bursal Disease (IBD) is an acute and highly contagious immunosuppressive disease that seriously threatens the poultry industry.&lt;SEP&gt;A specific disease that is targeted by the newly developed vaccine.&lt;SEP&gt;A disease, also known as IBD, whose occurrence in Ethiopia is being reported by the paper.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-66b9c03397d1767f2c8fe38e229f4281&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8e6a0c54d176872c8e2cb5eb5bad7b83&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c6e53de7a54e4357e1d8e18f10e13a45</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
