<node id="Very Virulent IBDV">
  <data key="d0">Very Virulent IBDV</data>
  <data key="d1">creature</data>
  <data key="d2">Very Virulent IBDV (vvIBDV) is a strain of Infectious Bursal Disease Virus characterized by high lethality, which has been a focus of prevention and control in China.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-66b9c03397d1767f2c8fe38e229f4281</data>
