  <data key="d0">IBDV Genotype A2dB1</data>
  <data key="d1">creature</data>
  <data key="d2">IBDV Genotype A2dB1 is a newly emerging Novel Variant IBDV, found in 52.0% of analyzed samples, and identified as an important epidemic strain in China.</data>
