  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Novel Epidemic Characteristics refer to the new patterns of spread and genotype distribution of Infectious Bursal Disease Virus, revealed by this study.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-66b9c03397d1767f2c8fe38e229f4281</data>
