  <data key="d0">Community-Based Mosquito Control Strategy</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">A strategy for mosquito control that resulted in the elimination of Aedes aegypti in 40 of 46 communes in northern and central Vietnam, with annual recurrent costs of $0.28–$0.89 international dollars per person.</data>
