<node id="The Study">
  <data key="d0">The Study</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">The scientific research detailed in the text, which involved developing a fluorescence labeling method and conducting co-culture and laboratory challenge tests to investigate biological control.&lt;SEP&gt;The study refers to the research conducted between 2005 and 2010 to investigate S. japonicum prevalence in domestic ruminants and field feces.&lt;SEP&gt;The study refers to the research presented in the text, which provides new insights into dengue's global burden.&lt;SEP&gt;A study that demonstrates the local abundance of Mesocyclops spp.</data>
