<node id="Vietnam">
  <data key="d0">Vietnam</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">The country where the pilot study was conducted, involving mosquito collection along a national road from its north end to the Mekong Delta.&lt;SEP&gt;Vietnam is a developing country where local veterinary centres often lack fume cupboards.&lt;SEP&gt;The country where the investigation regarding fish-borne trematodes took place.&lt;SEP&gt;Vietnam is a location where the mosquito control strategy is suggested to be sustainable.&lt;SEP&gt;Vietnam is the geographical location where the dogs were located for this study.&lt;SEP&gt;Vietnam is the geographical location where the study was conducted and where bed net use among children was observed to be high.&lt;SEP&gt;A country where clinical/pathophysiological studies are supported by Wellcome Trust and AFRIMS.</data>
