  <data key="d1">creature</data>
  <data key="d2">A species of parasite for which the POC-CCA assay should be adapted, critical for improved diagnostics in PR China's elimination phase.&lt;SEP&gt;A parasite against which antibodies are detected in buffaloes.&lt;SEP&gt;An organism against which antibodies are detected, and from which recombinant FBPA is derived.&lt;SEP&gt;A parasitic organism whose active infection is the target for detection by the anti-egg antigen IgG-ELISA.&lt;SEP&gt;A species of pathogen causing infection, detectable in animals.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9336f8ff47d41cf54524beadc73b8228&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-242cd5f8872ef5ebae9f67588eafd60b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-213dd01df1213177a022c154bb9c179e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d74bdf51589a721125f34efbec1c60b8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e469ec2af24bbc690574902269eceff1</data>
