<node id="Clonorchiasis">
  <data key="d0">Clonorchiasis</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Clonorchiasis is a parasitic disease caused by Clonorchis sinensis infection, which can be difficult to diagnose under certain circumstances like biliary tract obstruction or light infection.&lt;SEP&gt;A parasitic disease that can be accurately diagnosed using the multiplex PCR approach.&lt;SEP&gt;A disease whose transmission status can be evaluated.&lt;SEP&gt;Clonorchiasis is a parasitic disease or infection.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-acad4a812e7cbf80eff3b268dbc2646a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-73c7f0c924eada8686a75bb4a92f7f4f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c71b2b7d263cbd0f9713a997f17fdccd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-27cb4a5bb97ef3dfcbc5e83b0f45a8c4</data>
