<node id="Carbon-Fiber Spikes">
  <data key="d0">Carbon-Fiber Spikes</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Carbon-Fiber Spikes are a specialized and cutting-edge type of advanced sprinting footwear, explicitly designed for athletes competing in competitive athletics. These advanced sprinting shoes are engineered to provide enhanced speed and superior traction during athletic performance, making them a crucial piece of equipment for achieving peak performance and enhancing overall output in sprinting.

The high-level capabilities and effectiveness of Carbon-Fiber Spikes are significantly attributed to the incorporation of carbon fiber technology in their construction. This advanced material directly contributes to their ability to facilitate superior athletic output. A notable example highlighting their impact and advanced nature includes their use by athlete Noah Carter, who utilized Carbon-Fiber Spikes to break the 100m sprint record.&lt;SEP&gt;Carbon-fiber spikes are advanced sprinting shoes that provide enhanced speed and traction.&lt;SEP&gt;Carbon-fiber spikes are cutting-edge items used by Noah Carter to break the 100m sprint record.</data>
