  <data key="d2">The World Athletics Championship is a global sports competition that features top athletes in track and field disciplines. This prestigious event serves as a platform for elite competitors from around the world to showcase their skills and compete for records and titles.

A recent edition of the World Athletics Championship was held in Tokyo. During this particular event, a significant athletic milestone was achieved when Noah Carter successfully broke the 100m sprint record.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Championship is an event held in Tokyo where Noah Carter broke the 100m sprint record.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Championship is an event in Tokyo where Noah Carter broke the 100m sprint record.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Championship is a global sports competition featuring top athletes in track and field.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Championship is an event where Noah Carter broke the 100m sprint record.</data>
