  <data key="d2">PCR (Polymerase Chain Reaction) is a valuable and sensitive diagnostic tool.&lt;SEP&gt;A diagnostic method indicated as suitable for early diagnosis, evaluation of drug efficacy, and diagnosis of re-infection post-treatment.&lt;SEP&gt;PCR (Polymerase Chain Reaction) is a sensitive molecular biology technique identified as a promising tool for disease diagnostics and screening.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-012d2a1f54a9109b525d7616d0bdf665&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-30162a1defec7ca71236fd24fbcef8a3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5176eb820492c017bae55bd3d9afdaaf</data>
