  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">A type of parasitic infection that can be low-intensity, for which PCR is a valuable diagnostic tool.&lt;SEP&gt;O. Viverrini infection is a specific parasitic condition that can be diagnosed.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-012d2a1f54a9109b525d7616d0bdf665&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c4f0a5936dcb5c74c221d4f619d8f45a</data>
