<node id="Market Selloff">
  <data key="d0">Market Selloff</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">A Market Selloff refers to a significant decline in stock values across financial markets. This phenomenon is primarily driven by investor concerns, particularly regarding interest rates and regulatory changes.

A market selloff is characterized by a substantial downward movement in the value of stocks. While such an event can be observed on a specific day, as indicated by phrases like "observed today" or "faced by stock markets today," these refer to instances of a selloff rather than defining the concept itself. The underlying cause consistently points to apprehension among investors about economic and policy factors.&lt;SEP&gt;Market selloff refers to the significant decline in stock values due to investor concerns over interest rates and regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;Market selloff refers to the significant decline in stock values due to investor concerns over interest rates and regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;A significant market event characterized by a sharp downturn in stock values, attributed to investor concerns over rising interest rates and regulatory uncertainty.&lt;SEP&gt;Market selloff refers to the significant decline in stock values due to investor concerns over interest rates and regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;Market selloff refers to the significant decline in stock values due to investor concerns over interest rates and regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;A market selloff is a significant decline in stock values, attributed to investor concerns over rising interest rates and regulatory uncertainty.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-741c138905578052bbea5e72d3ce9cf7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2267b7d403708ba84d848c3e6ebdc424&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-de1dfa85f35198065a93de9b311c60b4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5cef9c26c71a9aaa6d5d31b93abccf82&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-902f25199a26ad8f7763d7d79a7578d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-73c7f0c924eada8686a75bb4a92f7f4f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-238c2e1b073d66f94b56266ab745be34&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-27cb4a5bb97ef3dfcbc5e83b0f45a8c4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c1aaa2470e7464a09774dbb42c1287e6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-80b97f9e924421f7263d201cc76d061b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4e38bf3bf822086eb0e754ae3929ef24&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f2be54d0de85f52c65a2ac2f0b33cdf7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6cd1108f1e79a8b6b9042081360f8b73&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-18dc28b186b69b4dc32fd45ae507f576&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8f67b4135b81382ee1dfd5329983fe84&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-32039222e39636a5625940ae62b86fb0</data>
