</node>
<node id="Interest Rates">
  <data key="d0">Interest Rates</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Interest rates are a factor causing investor concerns and attributed to the market selloff.&lt;SEP&gt;Interest rates are financial metrics, with rising rates contributing to investor concerns.&lt;SEP&gt;Interest rates are a key economic factor, with rising rates causing investor concerns and potential future hikes.&lt;SEP&gt;The cost of borrowing money, with rising rates being a concern for investors.&lt;SEP&gt;Interest rates are a financial factor, with rising rates contributing to investor concerns.&lt;SEP&gt;Interest rates are a key economic factor, with rising rates causing investor concerns.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-741c138905578052bbea5e72d3ce9cf7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2267b7d403708ba84d848c3e6ebdc424&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-902f25199a26ad8f7763d7d79a7578d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c1aaa2470e7464a09774dbb42c1287e6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4e38bf3bf822086eb0e754ae3929ef24&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-32039222e39636a5625940ae62b86fb0</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1768547202</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Regulatory Uncertainty">
  <data key="d0">Regulatory Uncertainty</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Regulatory Uncertainty refers to a state characterized by a lack of clarity, predictability, or ambiguity concerning government regulations, including those pertaining to future regulations and market operations. This condition represents an unpredictable regulatory environment.

As both an economic and market factor, regulatory uncertainty is a primary concern for investors. It is identified by analysts as a key contributing element to heightened investor concerns, which can significantly impact business operations and overall investor confidence. This lack of clarity regarding future regulations is further noted to contribute to market declines, broader market selloffs, and general market volatility.&lt;SEP&gt;Regulatory uncertainty refers to unpredictability in government regulations, contributing to investor concerns.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-741c138905578052bbea5e72d3ce9cf7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2267b7d403708ba84d848c3e6ebdc424&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-de1dfa85f35198065a93de9b311c60b4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5cef9c26c71a9aaa6d5d31b93abccf82&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-902f25199a26ad8f7763d7d79a7578d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-73c7f0c924eada8686a75bb4a92f7f4f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-238c2e1b073d66f94b56266ab745be34&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-27cb4a5bb97ef3dfcbc5e83b0f45a8c4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c1aaa2470e7464a09774dbb42c1287e6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-80b97f9e924421f7263d201cc76d061b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4e38bf3bf822086eb0e754ae3929ef24&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f2be54d0de85f52c65a2ac2f0b33cdf7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6cd1108f1e79a8b6b9042081360f8b73&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-18dc28b186b69b4dc32fd45ae507f576&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8f67b4135b81382ee1dfd5329983fe84&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-32039222e39636a5625940ae62b86fb0</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
