<node id="Rising Interest Rates">
  <data key="d0">Rising Interest Rates</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Rising interest rates refer to an economic trend or condition characterized by an increase in borrowing costs. This economic factor is widely identified by analysts and is a significant concern for investors, directly impacting investor sentiment and market valuations. The increase in borrowing costs associated with rising interest rates is a key contributor to heightened investor concerns and has been cited as a primary factor contributing to market selloffs.&lt;SEP&gt;Rising interest rates are an economic factor causing investor concerns and contributing to market volatility.&lt;SEP&gt;A factor contributing to investor concerns and the market selloff.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-de1dfa85f35198065a93de9b311c60b4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5cef9c26c71a9aaa6d5d31b93abccf82&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-73c7f0c924eada8686a75bb4a92f7f4f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-238c2e1b073d66f94b56266ab745be34&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-27cb4a5bb97ef3dfcbc5e83b0f45a8c4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-80b97f9e924421f7263d201cc76d061b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f2be54d0de85f52c65a2ac2f0b33cdf7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6cd1108f1e79a8b6b9042081360f8b73&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-18dc28b186b69b4dc32fd45ae507f576&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8f67b4135b81382ee1dfd5329983fe84</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1768547003</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Potential Rate Hikes">
  <data key="d0">Potential Rate Hikes</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Potential rate hikes are speculated actions by the Federal Reserve, influencing investor confidence.&lt;SEP&gt;Potential rate hikes are a subject of speculation regarding the Federal Reserve's next move.&lt;SEP&gt;Potential rate hikes are actions speculated to be taken by the Federal Reserve.&lt;SEP&gt;Possible increases in interest rates, speculated upon and watched by financial experts.&lt;SEP&gt;Potential rate hikes refer to speculative increases in interest rates by the Federal Reserve.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-de1dfa85f35198065a93de9b311c60b4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-238c2e1b073d66f94b56266ab745be34&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-27cb4a5bb97ef3dfcbc5e83b0f45a8c4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6cd1108f1e79a8b6b9042081360f8b73&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-18dc28b186b69b4dc32fd45ae507f576</data>
