  <data key="d0">Rising Oil Prices</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Rising oil prices contributed to Omega Energy's stock gain.&lt;SEP&gt;Rising oil prices are a factor that drove Omega Energy's stock gain.&lt;SEP&gt;Rising oil prices are a factor that drove a modest gain for Omega Energy.&lt;SEP&gt;An economic factor that drove the 2.1% gain in Omega Energy's stock.&lt;SEP&gt;Rising oil prices are an economic factor that drove Omega Energy's stock gain.&lt;SEP&gt;A factor that drove a modest gain for Omega Energy.</data>
