  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Virulence is the severity or harmfulness of a disease, which can be markedly increased in attenuated IBDV.&lt;SEP&gt;Virulence is a property of IBDV, whose markers are found to reside in VP2.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a24535c690694ea0dca88b58ffad8df3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3bd2462ffd61bc9c835e45ba219e87ca</data>
