  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Policy-Makers are individuals or groups responsible for creating and implementing policies relevant to public health, requiring information and persuasion regarding dengue.&lt;SEP&gt;Individuals responsible for creating and implementing public policies.</data>
