  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The Epidemiological Juncture refers to a critical point in the study of infectious, particularly viral, emerging diseases at the start of the 21st century.&lt;SEP&gt;A critical point in the study and control of disease outbreaks, describing the current situation for dengue.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-09f7b30a7a44fb488c4648dd1aaa96dc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a1d9f22d4827e48764fcb87e87f98a6e</data>
