  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Dengue Control refers to the efforts to manage and mitigate the disease, requiring a stronger voice from within dengue-endemic countries and the global public health community.&lt;SEP&gt;The objective of the community-based program, aimed at managing or eradicating dengue.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a1d9f22d4827e48764fcb87e87f98a6e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-09f7b30a7a44fb488c4648dd1aaa96dc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-155e703201f0d545bdedc2599eaf52a4</data>
