<node id="Severe Dengue Diagnosis">
  <data key="d0">Severe Dengue Diagnosis</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Severe Dengue Diagnosis involves standardized approaches for identifying severe forms of the disease using techniques like ultrasound, non-invasive technology, and laboratory markers.</data>
