<edge source="100m Sprint Record" target="Noah Carter">
  <data key="d7">13.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation "(100m Sprint Record, Noah Carter)" describes an athletic achievement. Noah Carter is noted for having established a new record in the 100-meter sprint event. This significant accomplishment took place at a championship event where Carter successfully broke the existing record.&lt;SEP&gt;Noah Carter set a new 100m sprint record at the championship.&lt;SEP&gt;Noah Carter set a new 100m sprint record at the championship.&lt;SEP&gt;Noah Carter set a new 100m sprint record at the championship.&lt;SEP&gt;Noah Carter broke the 100m sprint record.&lt;SEP&gt;Noah Carter broke the 100m sprint record.</data>
  <data key="d9">achievement,athlete achievement,broke,record-breaking</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-ad77c043b59272c028c58fbd6263f39a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04e148a1039e18d7262fc9c5d047f8ab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-794b1d58cb9a774ddce4478b53693842&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e8b42fd47496d3efb4bab267564a345d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d74bdf51589a721125f34efbec1c60b8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b242c81237407e520d835a20e3cc5dc4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-04ce53de96c9ce916467a7ca9f36d228&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0024b8ddacb751e7c5dc5f8d0ea108eb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-28ab4980ebe707c8dec2df7bbc3b467d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a39b82deb8ec634e1ebee4a2a6faefeb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3fc823099d0a6aa43191157d05a6250a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4a14c114d2071ce1f1b2720e241751ff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-defa4dbd529a4663ae47a157c6019fd5</data>
