<edge source="100m Sprint Record" target="Carbon-Fiber Spikes">
  <data key="d7">5.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Carbon-fiber spikes were used in the breaking of the 100m sprint record.&lt;SEP&gt;The 100m sprint record was broken with the use of carbon-fiber spikes.&lt;SEP&gt;Carbon-fiber spikes were used to achieve the 100m sprint record.&lt;SEP&gt;Carbon-fiber spikes were used to achieve the 100m sprint record.&lt;SEP&gt;Carbon-fiber spikes were used as cutting-edge technology to break the 100m sprint record.</data>
