<edge source="Carbon-Fiber Spikes" target="Noah Carter">
  <data key="d7">20.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation between Carbon-Fiber Spikes and Noah Carter indicates that Noah Carter is recognized for his utilization of carbon-fiber spikes. These spikes are described as cutting-edge equipment. Carter employed these advanced spikes with the specific intention of enhancing his performance during a race. His consistent use of this technology underscores a deliberate strategy to gain a competitive advantage in his athletic endeavors.&lt;SEP&gt;Noah Carter used cutting-edge carbon-fiber spikes.&lt;SEP&gt;Noah Carter used carbon-fiber spikes to enhance performance during the race.&lt;SEP&gt;Noah Carter used cutting-edge carbon-fiber spikes.&lt;SEP&gt;Noah Carter used carbon-fiber spikes.&lt;SEP&gt;Noah Carter used carbon-fiber spikes when he broke the 100m sprint record.</data>
  <data key="d9">athletic artifact,athletic equipment,equipment,performance boost,usage,used</data>
