<edge source="Global Tech Index" target="Market Selloff">
  <data key="d7">9.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation "(Global Tech Index, Market Selloff)" describes a situation where the Global Tech Index is experiencing a decline as a component of a broader market selloff. This broader market downturn is driven primarily by investor concerns.

Specifically, the Global Tech Index has been observed dropping by 3.4%, which indicates its active participation in the wider market selloff. Therefore, the decline in the Global Tech Index is considered an integral part of this larger market event.&lt;SEP&gt;The Global Tech Index experienced a decline as part of the broader market selloff.</data>
