  <data key="d8">The relation between Global Tech Index and Nexon Technologies describes an instance where the stock performance of Nexon Technologies influenced the broader market index. Specifically, a decline in Nexon Technologies' stock was identified as a contributing factor to an overall drop observed in the Global Tech Index.

Furthermore, it is noted that this decline in Nexon Technologies' stock contributed significantly to the aforementioned decrease in the Global Tech Index. This indicates a notable impact from Nexon Technologies' individual stock performance on the aggregate index.</data>
