<edge source="Federal Reserve Policy Announcement" target="Investor Confidence">
  <data key="d7">16.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation between Federal Reserve Policy Announcement and Investor Confidence signifies that the actions and statements made by the Federal Reserve regarding its monetary policy are anticipated to have a direct impact on the level of investor confidence. Specifically, a Federal Reserve policy announcement is generally expected to influence how investors perceive critical economic indicators, including market stability, future economic growth, and the availability of investment opportunities. These perceptions, in turn, affect investors' overall confidence in the financial markets and the broader economy.&lt;SEP&gt;The Federal Reserve's upcoming policy announcement is expected to influence investor confidence.</data>
  <data key="d9">expectation,expected influence,impact,influence,market factor,market impact,market influence,market outlook,market sentiment,policy impact</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-741c138905578052bbea5e72d3ce9cf7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2267b7d403708ba84d848c3e6ebdc424&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-de1dfa85f35198065a93de9b311c60b4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5cef9c26c71a9aaa6d5d31b93abccf82&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-902f25199a26ad8f7763d7d79a7578d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-73c7f0c924eada8686a75bb4a92f7f4f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-238c2e1b073d66f94b56266ab745be34&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-27cb4a5bb97ef3dfcbc5e83b0f45a8c4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c1aaa2470e7464a09774dbb42c1287e6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-80b97f9e924421f7263d201cc76d061b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4e38bf3bf822086eb0e754ae3929ef24&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f2be54d0de85f52c65a2ac2f0b33cdf7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6cd1108f1e79a8b6b9042081360f8b73&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-18dc28b186b69b4dc32fd45ae507f576&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8f67b4135b81382ee1dfd5329983fe84&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-32039222e39636a5625940ae62b86fb0</data>
