<edge source="Investor Concerns" target="Rising Interest Rates">
  <data key="d7">9.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Rising interest rates constitute a prominent factor contributing to investor concerns. These concerns are frequently heightened, driven by, and specifically linked to the prospect of increasing interest rates. This apprehension over rising interest rates is considered a primary investor concern, and has been identified as a contributing element to market events such as a selloff.&lt;SEP&gt;Investor concerns are over rising interest rates.</data>
