  <data key="d8">Rising oil prices have been consistently identified as the primary catalyst behind a gain experienced by Omega Energy. This positive performance for Omega Energy is directly attributable to the upward trend in oil prices. The gain has been specifically noted as a "stock gain" in some instances, and on other occasions, described as a "modest gain," indicating a positive but potentially limited financial improvement for the company.&lt;SEP&gt;Omega Energy's stock gain was driven by rising oil prices.&lt;SEP&gt;Omega Energy posted a gain driven by rising oil prices.</data>
