<edge source="Federal Reserve" target="Financial Experts">
  <data key="d7">14.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relationship between the Federal Reserve and financial experts is defined by a consistent and close scrutiny from the latter. Financial experts are actively and closely watching the Federal Reserve's activities and decisions. This observation specifically extends to anticipating the Federal Reserve's next moves and understanding the implications of its various actions.&lt;SEP&gt;Financial experts are closely watching the Federal Reserve's next move.&lt;SEP&gt;Financial experts are closely watching the Federal Reserve.&lt;SEP&gt;Financial experts are closely watching the Federal Reserve's next move.&lt;SEP&gt;Financial experts are closely watching the Federal Reserve's next move.&lt;SEP&gt;Financial experts are closely watching the Federal Reserve's next move.&lt;SEP&gt;Financial experts are closely watching the Federal Reserve's next move.</data>
