<edge source="Federal Reserve" target="Rate Hikes">
  <data key="d7">9.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relationship between the Federal Reserve and rate hikes signifies the ongoing situation where the Federal Reserve is actively considering potential increases to interest rates. There is significant and growing speculation among observers and markets regarding these prospective rate hikes. Consequently, the Federal Reserve is being closely watched for any indications or definitive decisions related to adjusting interest rates upwards.&lt;SEP&gt;Speculation is growing over potential rate hikes by the Federal Reserve.</data>
